2. pitch shift , support color auxiliary prompt (green, orange, red, respectively, to indicate the impact of the change of key on the sound quality);
3. speed adjustment to multiply the speed display, while showing the beat speed (BPM);
4. independent adjustment of modulation and speed change, do not affect each other ;
